articles.description: Nico Carvacho had a career-high 26 points and a career-high-tying 20 rebounds to help Colorado State beat San Jose State 90-79 on Saturday.
articles.headline: Colorado State snaps 7-game skid with 3rd-string coach

articles.description: Jarrell Brantley scored 30 points, Nick Harris added 21, both career highs, and College of Charleston rolled to an 89-67 win over Drexel on Saturday for its eighth-straight win.
articles.headline: Charleston avenges loss, defeats Drexel 89-67

articles.description: An emotional Tom Izzo explains how Michigan State got the game-winning basket and why this game vs. Purdue meant a little more.
articles.headline: Izzo on final shot: 'We wanted to get it to Bridges'

images.caption: An emotional Tom Izzo explains how Michigan State got the game-winning basket and why this game vs. Purdue meant a little more.
images.name: Izzo on final shot: 'We wanted to get it to Bridges'

articles.description: Marin Maric scored 18 points, Tre'Darius McCallum added 12 points and 10 rebounds and DePaul cruised to an 80-63 victory over Providence on Saturday.
articles.headline: DePaul rolls in 80-63 victory over Providence

articles.description: Kahlil Dukes scored 22 points, Marvin Prochet and Matt Scott each had double-doubles and Niagara pulled away in the second half to beat Fairfield 95-83 on Saturday.
articles.headline: Niagara pulls away in second half, beats Fairfield 95-83
